{"tid":253114,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得生活辛苦好攰嘅同我入晒黎","createTime":"2017-05-22T06:34:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T19:23:28.000Z","uid":104075,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f407b607aae441eb5c9845a1fe372664b382d880","tid":253114,"uid":104075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T06:34:34.000Z","msg":"無論你係返工對住老細頂佢唔順又好<br />\n做嘢做到死死氣唔想再做落去又好<br />\n依家捱更抵夜溫緊書都好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">真心想講聲辛苦你啦！加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如果你覺得無人支持你無人明白你<br />\n唔緊要仲有我！雖然素未謀面同大家三唔識七<br />\n不過都想俾啲正能量大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  或者分擔下煩惱<br />\n<br />\n如果你想搵個人傾下心事<br />\n可以打字俾我或者錄音比我<br />\n我都係個唔錯嘅傾訴對象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我唔會好似班old seafood咁扮晒嘢講埋晒啲人生建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果你需要一個人為你做理性分析嘅話就唔好搵我啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Heartwindow\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHeartwindow&d=WsZpLEGudxUbfaIdpI%2FiYv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=bb044a89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Heartwindow</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好問我係絲定係巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我只係一個樹窿<br />\n要求偶出返去交友app<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fb897189ef0fbf40d647b199af23d180063ff52","tid":253114,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T06:35:23.000Z","msg":"完sem 好頹"},{"pid":"47fd540472be96b1ac5002e04ee28ff39fa5ac22","tid":253114,"uid":7843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T06:35:56.000Z","msg":"毒撚唔敢搵你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"337b160b3fcc921c6b5b45cff0eadbc5c2ad0370","tid":253114,"uid":90045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T07:19:02.000Z","msg":"